{"tid":264081,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"人在捷克 被偷銀包 繼續行程定走","createTime":"2017-05-30T14:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T16:19:02.000Z","uid":41523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87f3c893c2289632ee7d0043e7506aad5247ebe1","tid":264081,"uid":41523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"原定行程 Prague Cesky Krumlov Salzburg Vienna Budapest 返去Prague 最後Amsterdam走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家係Cesky Krumlov 今朝Prague被偷銀包 信用卡提款卡身份證冇哂 得護照係身 叫香港朋友幫手打哂電話Cut哂卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n旅保唔包自己中間唔繼續落去買機票走 繼續落去只係$$既問題 係解決到既 只係自己心情不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCost黎講 繼續落去 5Xxx 走 7000內返到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇經歷過既朋友講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32a049d66bece522403ccb6ea6525a2174b7313","tid":264081,"uid":41523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原定行程 Prague Cesky Krumlov Salzburg Vienna Budapest 返去Prague 最後Amsterdam走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家係Cesky Krumlov 今朝Prague被偷銀包 信用卡提款卡身份證冇哂 得護照係身 叫香港朋友幫手打哂電話Cut哂卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n旅保唔包自己中間唔繼續落去買機票走 繼續落去只係$$既問題 係解決到既 只係自己心情不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCost黎講 繼續落去 5Xxx 走 7000內返到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇經歷過既朋友講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係Prague地鐵比人撞1撞自己又死蠢放銀包係褲袋 懷疑係咁就比人M左去 已報案"},{"pid":"116ca1df4168c42b16f17c707f2716cb651e34c7","tid":264081,"uid":20270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:06:53.000Z","msg":"你咁講如果有錢係身無理由走啦"},{"pi