"tid":264081,"uid":6675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>旅保唔包自己？<br />\n咁俾人偷左銀包即係返到黎都冇得claim?</blockquote><br />\n返到黎可以Claim 係如果我依家返香港 自費走人 冇得Claim個舊$$ 個心好唔安落 但客觀上繼續冇影響個行程</blockquote><br />\n安心玩埋佢<br />\n你都冇野俾人偷了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927535638111ed097d7dc1f11135815f6051ceee","tid":264081,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:32:21.000Z","msg":"有得claim就繼續玩啦，難得搭咁耐飛機一場去到，冇理由乘興而去敗興而返"},{"pid":"4aae7228dcbdadb89ae5af5bec4d821a237fefdd","tid":264081,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"去叫雞出下火先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9bfcc11c1f445dc94f34019948f5c01be9e58d","tid":264081,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"玩埋佢啦<br />\n有朋友係到唔驚啦"},{"pid":"30898244e90d2fe2ace192c2dc2fc618710ee95e","tid":264081,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"你啲錢分開左放？玩埋去啦，反正都過到去，你改機票又要比錢咁煩，你住啲hotel又可能無得cancel，得都要搞一輪，算啦，唔發生都發生左"},{"pid":"9e16ad798b2f28c8402ee657a0a80db8d4442d14","tid":264081,"uid":59707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"最差嘅嘢你都遇過，即係跟住落黎一定係好事，玩埋佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1a1ece2b29e307f8a1f43404afbd9facb18dd8","tid":264081,"uid":66954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:26:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最差嘅嘢你都遇過，即係跟住落黎一定係好事，玩埋佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同，過幾個月回顧返只係得啖笑，<br />\n識個女仔喺埃成個大背包無咗，報警都無用，所有行季無哂喊完繼續行程 (買過d衫用日用品)，喺歐洲旅行識佢，佢當故事咁講返出來，佢話已經無野可以再衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我旅行遇到咩黑仔野，我都諗起佢，感覺好一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff9bda1624210debd76b460913b243f01bcfc81","tid":264081,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:28:33.000Z","msg":"下次銀包唔好放褲袋喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學精咗，唔好比人有機會下手就邊度都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58afe20428ea7c8eb1bcafcf946637339117dec","tid":264081,"uid":3146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:33:08.000Z","msg":"之前去prague都係將錢分開放 仲要用belt bag放係衫入面"},{"pid":"99e5312b4d230d1a0d99e54e74ada4bdc57b0d5d","tid":264081,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"我啱啱係布拉格走<br />\n個度出左名多小偷...巴打你真係..."},{"pid":"ad104d06d026a43fc041ba51429723a207723755","tid":264081,"uid":1970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:48:46.000Z","msg":"識人係希臘比人偷左個袋，passport 銀包相機ipad 講得出既重要野都冇哂，得返大backpack一袋衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過整返passport 都繼續行程 <br />\n乜撚都冇都試過啦，冇咩可以再衰，點解唔繼續？<br />\n你都係冇左個銀包姐，其他野尚健在，咪繼續行程囉，最多叫屋企人west union 匯錢/問朋友借住先"},{"pid":"905ff6746ea0aa3418a45e99b754215521a70bce","tid":264081,"uid":107271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己定同朋友一齊去？<br />\n申利 2月去布拉格 落柏林 再去 克拉科夫 上返布拉格走 第一日落機唔見哂野 得返護照</blockquote><br />\nChing咁妳點搞得掂個行程</blockquote><br />\n金錢上好在有班兄弟撐住 網上過錢落班fd戶口 當地禁返出黎 走個陣因為我自己返港 借左人張信用卡傍身 其實最難搞都係心情姐 你既然有錢可以繼續 你冇理由走扔低你個旅伴既 落樓下食返個布拉格出名既雪糕先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b244bbb5143e2774884ac9c4be335ef93da136","tid":264081,"uid":41523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:17:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前去prague都係將錢分開放 仲要用belt bag放係衫入面</blockquote><br />\n不可一不可再 會警剔返"},{"pid":"4fa26cf7f2f60054e6996ba81a0486fabae06900","tid":264081,"uid":41523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:17:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己定同朋友一齊去？<br />\n申利 2月去布拉格 落柏林 再去 克拉科夫 上返布拉格走 第一日落機唔見哂野 得返護照</blockquote><br />\nChing咁妳點搞得掂個行程</blockquote><br />\n金錢上好在有班兄弟撐住 網上過錢落班fd戶口 當地禁返出黎 走個陣因為我自己返港 借左人張信用卡傍身 其實最難搞都係心情姐 你既然有錢可以繼續 你冇理由走扔低你個旅伴既 落樓下食返個布拉格出名既雪糕先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冧通左 捱下去奮力去追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcd6eaaabfbbe0df13ad7c5d49ab6aa9bc14537","tid":264081,"uid":41523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識人係希臘比人偷左個袋，passport 銀包相機ipad 講得出既重要野都冇哂，得返大backpack一袋衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過整返passport 都繼續行程 <br />\n乜撚都冇都試過啦，冇咩可以再衰，點解唔繼續？<br />\n你都係冇左個銀包姐，其他野尚健在，咪繼續行程囉，最多叫屋企人west union 匯錢/問朋友借住先</blockquote><br />\n琴日個心情係覺得語言不通好驚搞唔掂 搵返香港朋友幫手報失Cut信用卡 之後其實都醒覺根本唔算得係乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同係香港唔見銀包1樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所有用$$解決到既其實都唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/142151_07b38ed4f23bc734c5228223a43baf66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F142151_07b38ed4f23bc734c5228223a43baf66.jpg&h=a5cf609d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/142155_753c65c9348dc5ea1aa2860cb81fca29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F142155_753c65c9348dc5ea1aa2860cb81fca29.jpg&h=6817c384&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/142159_d2bc2657b0a1746ce77eb385a50e225a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F142159_d2bc2657b0a1746ce77eb385a50e225a.jpg&h=db75c4e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/142202_c6fb4ec0aab99dd06969f68246d45a88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F142202_c6fb4ec0aab99dd06969f68246d45a88.jpg&h=207fdf4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21a0872e77c366837ef2b97a385bb662e3f469b0","tid":264081,"uid":66340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"歐洲真係幾靚都無用<br />\n小偷多到痴線<br />\n仲勁過東南亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccc4f1b05491e5f29fc389c31caa8855226340a","tid":264081,"uid":18869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:25:07.000Z","msg":"巴打銀包放褲袋咩位？ 咁易拎？"},{"pid":"2237ee38b1f948cd83ccb64b95707cc2bc1e5be8","tid":264081,"uid":41523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打銀包放褲袋咩位？ 咁易拎？</blockquote><br />\n事緣係咁 <br />\n我同個伴出地鐵 道門唔開 有個男人幫我地用手開門 以為佢幫左我個伴出 我都冇事啦 係我死蠢以為佢係幫我 佢係幫我開個陣撞埋黎我到 跟住後面有個男人應該就落左手偷我褲袋既銀包 大家要小心呢種方法偷野 我返返Prague應該手機都放返入褸內袋 熱都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53af61f31d845f47da0b53c23e0716186a4ee80","tid":264081,"uid":41523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐洲真係幾靚都無用<br />\n小偷多到痴線<br />\n仲勁過東南亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黎完今次歐洲 當買個教訓 返到香港又好 下次去邊到旅行都好 銀包1定要收好 唔可以貪方便放褲袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0f14f0c9351d9c60ae64e8d0f2135904d7ba1e","tid":264081,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:37:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"979ef07588299fe0d86ae60a1ebcfda497a55394","tid":264081,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:38:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"142e9cf8d014a48cc1fc2350f4ecac4a22016ac2","tid":264081,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:44:06.000Z","msg":"我上次去捷克俾人雞姦，第日報完警都照繼續玩<br />\n巴打你唔見野算係咩"},{"pid":"f6588d6107dc2f128e8fa5805f78f91d2355c7d2","tid":264081,"uid":118068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:45:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4462c32eb578278ebc110ddc82fd0ccb62a5cd17","tid":264081,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:48:30.000Z","msg":"我之前去捷克一到埗就俾人偷銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩證件卡分開放<br />\n淨係唔見咗錢"},{"pid":"9bfc1f3fb541aeae196f1a7de81fee513c46be04","tid":264081,"uid":78887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:52:16.000Z","msg":"樓主嗰日個天好靚喎<br />\n<br />\nCK我都去過 好優美嘅小鎮<br />\n<br />\n難得去到真係唔好走！"},{"pid":"7048133d91cc50462b3359fdd3b8c4ccb5a85cb2","tid":264081,"uid":98680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上次去捷克俾人雞姦，第日報完警都照繼續玩<br />\n巴打你唔見野算係咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccacd9ba6bf841cd67bf689ee59538e117244f5","tid":264081,"uid":6537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我上次去捷克俾人雞姦，第日報完警都照繼續玩<br />\n巴打你唔見野算係咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勵志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21885e1b0cd6820b3d5e8aaef65e70f5357b7a8","tid":264081,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上次去捷克俾人雞姦，第日報完警都照繼續玩<br />\n巴打你唔見野算係咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcaba28913503651da709e63046771de9f147ab","tid":264081,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我上次去捷克俾人雞姦，第日報完警都照繼續玩<br />\n巴打你唔見野算係咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />more"},{"pid":"a68db3b2f257b0197b69bfff172de8998b38eba6","tid":264081,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:50:56.000Z","msg":"黎緊都會去 有d驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我銀包會放背囊入面 應該唔會比人偷到掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手機放前褲袋"},{"pid":"2adb9c4acedf99e6e4cebc9f47f3bf66249418ea","tid":264081,"uid":41523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊都會去 有d驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我銀包會放背囊入面 應該唔會比人偷到掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手機放前褲袋</blockquote><br />\n褲袋我已經唔敢再擺貴重野"},{"pid":"e86606992d273b7e911b603fb69061a0389d85b3","tid":264081,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T08:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我上次去捷克俾人雞姦，第日報完警都照繼續玩<br />\n巴打你唔見野算係咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />more</blockquote><br />\n之前air bnb<br />\n去到往左一陣無電<br />\n個鬼婆話要我賠錢整返d電<br />\n我講大話話係窮遊 無錢<br />\n之後佢話you have no money 。you have to do something as payment <br />\n<br />\n之後要奶佢個西先有電"},{"pid":"411c4869a4e2818dfd4f23e8539aed5ad9c45dfc","tid":264081,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T08:19:51.000Z","msg":"之前去土耳其俾人用架餐行住老笠，報完警落左案再繼續玩，爸打唔見錢算好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbe3626e6d5bb127b912d46fdb8f6b82d57e28e","tid":264081,"uid":41523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T18:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我上次去捷克俾人雞姦，第日報完警都照繼續玩<br />\n巴打你唔見野算係咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />more</blockquote><br />\n之前air bnb<br />\n去到往左一陣無電<br />\n個鬼婆話要我賠錢整返d電<br />\n我講大話話係窮遊 無錢<br />\n之後佢話you have no money 。you have to do something as payment <br />\n<br />\n之後要奶佢個西先有電</blockquote><br />\nChing Sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be27cd658dd9099ea695a779fd56d7acd17410a9","tid":264081,"uid":114114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T21:17:37.000Z","msg":"歐洲好多小偷，特別係巴士地鐵<br />\n佢地通常一班人行動，坐地鐵最好袋咩前，<br />\n如果咩後佢地好快會開你袋，<br />\n通埋小心電話，唔好掛住玩電話，<br />\n有d真係會就咁搶。"},{"pid":"e8dafac78f69f8762bc255eb28494a5c813b4167","tid":264081,"uid":16113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T21:59:05.000Z","msg":"人在Prague, 早幾日都都去完CK, Salzburg 等地方，銀包證件都放係細斜咩袋同埋攬係前邊，暫時無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Prague 真係好多人，唔好貪方便求其放銀包，佢地好多時集體行動，你唔會覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩係前邊係就係柒，但安全好多，一係好似上邊巴打咁講，買個money belt 放係入邊"},{"pid":"ed310773d765af23d6ae613c9ecda005077d966f","tid":264081,"uid":51744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T22:03:51.000Z","msg":"出街拎得越少越好，始終人生路不熟，一定被人盯實做目標搵機會落手。有一次係里斯本，屋企人行前我某一距離跟後，見到一對扒手情侶打我媽背囊主意，我即刻叫我阿媽，佢好自然回頭望吓我，果對扒手先至落唔到手。<br />\n<br />\n通常我係兩手空空，相機、約二三百蚊港紙等值當地貨幣、一張信用卡、香港身份證／護照，係咁多，連銀包都無帶出街，所有嘢袋咗係牛仔褲前面兩個袋，銀包實在有太多重要但旅行毋需嘅財物，一定被人吼住落手。就算被佢地偷晒都係好少數目。<br />\n<br />\n唔好因為咁樣而唔去旅行，為咗個扒手掃自己興。  反而，經一事長一智，下次小心啲就無問題啦。"},{"pid":"6818be4c596208adb827373e5f535f9bbcbc56fa","tid":264081,"uid":84460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T22:04:43.000Z","msg":"之前係愛爾蘭第1日就比人偷銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似巴打你咁<br />\n跌左差不多$1000<br />\n又卡又ID 係 passport無事<br />\n最後繼續行程 不過旅遊保claim得翻$600only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後好好彩係警局搵翻個銀包但無曬D 錢<br />\n同個銀包比人踩左好多腳<br />\n<br />\n不過想同你講 難得去到就繼續行程啦"},{"pid":"2efbd26f5cb5d8f63df9f091f8123a35b957f938","tid":264081,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T22:37:09.000Z","msg":"係西班牙南部中<br />\n失晒魂<br />\n唔知醒走巴士<br />\n信錯上網blog miss左免費入church時間<br />\n唔小心漏左衫 大毛巾 耳筒 係第2間hostel<br />\n啱啱又跌左個尿袋<br />\n出發又帶漏勁多野<br />\n因為垃圾ctrip 俄羅斯飛瑞典行李畀多成千蚊hkd<br />\n<br />\n自問算開朗 成日阿Q精神 <br />\n走巴士就同自己講 可能個班巴士會有意外會塞車  <br />\n<br />\n漏左野就同自己講 行李咁樣咁輕d囉 <br />\n<br />\n唔見左尿袋就同自己講 至少岩岩手機得返8%咁危急 用到最後一次 <br />\n<br />\n今日行去hostel要行山行幾十分鐘 夜晚行到畀狗追 兩隻大狗勁快跑黎追住我吠 我嚇到喊左出聲 都仲同自己講 好彩隻狗吠你 唔係你就行錯路啦<br />\n<br />\n我已經keep住日日咁樣安慰自己 但係都仲係好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一出發已經帶漏左用開張信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所有野都好唔順利 全部都好小事 但加加埋埋好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n之前係俄羅斯因為行李單野唔開心到係機場喊<br />\n<br />\n自問我日行多善 點解咁唔順利<br />\n<br />\n其實我off晒topic，不過想搵個地方呻下<br />\n不過至少我銀包電話相機都仲未唔見<br />\n<br />\nbtw 之前我直頭成個行李寄失左 荷蘭飛瑞典<br />\n個陣係瑞典讀緊書<br />\n所有手信 新衫（係荷蘭買既 tag都未拆啊屌）舊衫 胸圍底衫 乜乜柒柒 全部唔見晒<br />\nhand carry個backpack得d濕鳩荷蘭餅同貴重物品<br />\n身上仲著住荷蘭kingsday套核突橙色衫<br />\n個陣好似都唔開心左一個星期 係瑞典邊買新衫邊喊<br />\n<br />\n之前係捷克唔多覺有賊<br />\n反而巴打係amesterdam要小心d 紅燈區果頭 多賊到你唔信"},{"pid":"aea2ec453fe5ed54d85bdca02b019de5c962e448","tid":264081,"uid":84871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T22:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係西班牙南部中<br />\n失晒魂<br />\n唔知醒走巴士<br />\n信錯上網blog miss左免費入church時間<br />\n唔小心漏左衫 大毛巾 耳筒 係第2間hostel<br />\n啱啱又跌左個尿袋<br />\n出發又帶漏勁多野<br />\n因為垃圾ctrip 俄羅斯飛瑞典行李畀多成千蚊hkd<br />\n<br />\n自問算開朗 成日阿Q精神 <br />\n走巴士就同自己講 可能個班巴士會有意外會塞車  <br />\n<br />\n漏左野就同自己講 行李咁樣咁輕d囉 <br />\n<br />\n唔見左尿袋就同自己講 至少岩岩手機得返8%咁危急 用到最後一次 <br />\n<br />\n今日行去hostel要行山行幾十分鐘 夜晚行到畀狗追 兩隻大狗勁快跑黎追住我吠 我嚇到喊左出聲 都仲同自己講 好彩隻狗吠你 唔係你就行錯路啦<br />\n<br />\n我已經keep住日日咁樣安慰自己 但係都仲係好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一出發已經帶漏左用開張信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所有野都好唔順利 全部都好小事 但加加埋埋好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n之前係俄羅斯因為行李單野唔開心到係機場喊<br />\n<br />\n自問我日行多善 點解咁唔順利<br />\n<br />\n其實我off晒topic，不過想搵個地方呻下<br />\n不過至少我銀包電話相機都仲未唔見<br />\n<br />\nbtw 之前我直頭成個行李寄失左 荷蘭飛瑞典<br />\n個陣係瑞典讀緊書<br />\n所有手信 新衫（係荷蘭買既 tag都未拆啊屌）舊衫 胸圍底衫 乜乜柒柒 全部唔見晒<br />\nhand carry個backpack得d濕鳩荷蘭餅同貴重物品<br />\n身上仲著住荷蘭kingsday套核突橙色衫<br />\n個陣好似都唔開心左一個星期 係瑞典邊買新衫邊喊<br />\n<br />\n之前係捷克唔多覺有賊<br />\n反而巴打係amesterdam要小心d 紅燈區果頭 多賊到你唔信</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁慘"},{"pid":"2a89a237ed7932e893e46cd85a3dc70d6b45eec1","tid":264081,"uid":102909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:07:24.000Z","msg":"咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家人在Prague 準備聽日去Vienna 我上個月我朋友都係prague既hostel偷哂d野"},{"pid":"d8dbfa2d27fb758e08473dda7873e125965952fe","tid":264081,"uid":4070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:13:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"610f954c771b8cb2d64a8c6a8ee06f5c92fbd4c0","tid":264081,"uid":43991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:14:19.000Z","msg":"用開冇拉鏈嘅背囊<br />\n啫係索繩再加兩個扣嗰隻<br />\n我個銀包會放喺背囊暗格<br />\n散紙包放喺前褲袋<br />\n入面放二十歐<br />\n夠食夠區內交通<br />\n<br />\n當然自己警覺性都要有<br />\n特別去啲多人嘅景點"},{"pid":"c6f7d8cd22884c3fae91522eba1cc112de185d8d","tid":264081,"uid":43991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:16:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家人在Prague 準備聽日去Vienna 我上個月我朋友都係prague既hostel偷哂d野</blockquote><br />\n你朋友放啲咩喺hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb55f088e8a8c7c0813ebc9c513b8f04a5f84d76","tid":264081,"uid":102909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家人在Prague 準備聽日去Vienna 我上個月我朋友都係prague既hostel偷哂d野</blockquote><br />\n你朋友放啲咩喺hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMacBook 相機都冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b221921764b46cc137044cee628241ed68ae46","tid":264081,"uid":112514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:22:07.000Z","msg":"Cesky Krumlov 靚到仆街 去啦"},{"pid":"39b5959a99fb9c0bb4e7f8459e046c6560d5cb1b","tid":264081,"uid":30471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:32:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>旅保唔包自己？<br />\n咁俾人偷左銀包即係返到黎都冇得claim?</blockquote><br />\n返到黎可以Claim 係如果我依家返香港 自費走人 冇得Claim個舊$$ 個心好唔安落 但客觀上繼續冇影響個行程</blockquote><br />\n安心玩埋佢<br />\n你都冇野俾人偷了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩埋佢喇 反正你未必會再黎第二次"},{"pid":"1485ba050e70cefcdaa303522198caa5aee690ae","tid":264081,"uid":4517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:20:35.000Z","msg":"我老豆之前又係喺praha 偷銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲差佬根本唔想理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c09df3430c9a36ce6b893cbe82e190f69eae3d","tid":264081,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係西班牙南部中<br />\n失晒魂<br />\n唔知醒走巴士<br />\n信錯上網blog miss左免費入church時間<br />\n唔小心漏左衫 大毛巾 耳筒 係第2間hostel<br />\n啱啱又跌左個尿袋<br />\n出發又帶漏勁多野<br />\n因為垃圾ctrip 俄羅斯飛瑞典行李畀多成千蚊hkd<br />\n<br />\n自問算開朗 成日阿Q精神 <br />\n走巴士就同自己講 可能個班巴士會有意外會塞車  <br />\n<br />\n漏左野就同自己講 行李咁樣咁輕d囉 <br />\n<br />\n唔見左尿袋就同自己講 至少岩岩手機得返8%咁危急 用到最後一次 <br />\n<br />\n今日行去hostel要行山行幾十分鐘 夜晚行到畀狗追 兩隻大狗勁快跑黎追住我吠 我嚇到喊左出聲 都仲同自己講 好彩隻狗吠你 唔係你就行錯路啦<br />\n<br />\n我已經keep住日日咁樣安慰自己 但係都仲係好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一出發已經帶漏左用開張信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所有野都好唔順利 全部都好小事 但加加埋埋好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n之前係俄羅斯因為行李單野唔開心到係機場喊<br />\n<br />\n自問我日行多善 點解咁唔順利<br />\n<br />\n其實我off晒topic，不過想搵個地方呻下<br />\n不過至少我銀包電話相機都仲未唔見<br />\n<br />\nbtw 之前我直頭成個行李寄失左 荷蘭飛瑞典<br />\n個陣係瑞典讀緊書<br />\n所有手信 新衫（係荷蘭買既 tag都未拆啊屌）舊衫 胸圍底衫 乜乜柒柒 全部唔見晒<br />\nhand carry個backpack得d濕鳩荷蘭餅同貴重物品<br />\n身上仲著住荷蘭kingsday套核突橙色衫<br />\n個陣好似都唔開心左一個星期 係瑞典邊買新衫邊喊<br />\n<br />\n之前係捷克唔多覺有賊<br />\n反而巴打係amesterdam要小心d 紅燈區果頭 多賊到你唔信</blockquote><br />\n你e種係on"},{"pid":"a08cf48e7af7baf128948a0daa06fbdb0673c821","tid":264081,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:49:51.000Z","msg":"有冇人會用e度防盜背囊<br />\n好似幾正<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2016/05/19/montmartre/life-tech/travel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2016%2F05%2F19%2Fmontmartre%2Flife-tech%2Ftravel%2F&d=0P5qt6yvWKnFvwGVk4QO0P1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=00b6dcc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2016/05/19/montmartre/life-tech/travel/</a>"},{"pid":"9931261638a0f57a510137528062492d9521c922","tid":264081,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:50:56.000Z","msg":"老老實實點係歐洲防賊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n銀包放返前褲袋夠唔夠做?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ce400b2889507679da52c370ec439e542755e9","tid":264081,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:52:33.000Z","msg":"去過praha冇事, 淨係銀包放前褲袋+雙手插袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790e334c32c3eb63e19e6d0683521b2481eb5b0e","tid":264081,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T01:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我上次去捷克俾人雞姦，第日報完警都照繼續玩<br />\n巴打你唔見野算係咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />more</blockquote><br />\n之前air bnb<br />\n去到往左一陣無電<br />\n個鬼婆話要我賠錢整返d電<br />\n我講大話話係窮遊 無錢<br />\n之後佢話you have no money 。you have to do something as payment <br />\n<br />\n之後要奶佢個西先有電</blockquote><br />\nwa屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽你語氣個鬼妹肯定唔掂"},{"pid":"73084d5ed5286281db36217cd83b9585d9bdb9e7","tid":264081,"uid":61499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T01:12:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係西班牙南部中<br />\n失晒魂<br />\n唔知醒走巴士<br />\n信錯上網blog miss左免費入church時間<br />\n唔小心漏左衫 大毛巾 耳筒 係第2間hostel<br />\n啱啱又跌左個尿袋<br />\n出發又帶漏勁多野<br />\n因為垃圾ctrip 俄羅斯飛瑞典行李畀多成千蚊hkd<br />\n<br />\n自問算開朗 成日阿Q精神 <br />\n走巴士就同自己講 可能個班巴士會有意外會塞車  <br />\n<br />\n漏左野就同自己講 行李咁樣咁輕d囉 <br />\n<br />\n唔見左尿袋就同自己講 至少岩岩手機得返8%咁危急 用到最後一次 <br />\n<br />\n今日行去hostel要行山行幾十分鐘 夜晚行到畀狗追 兩隻大狗勁快跑黎追住我吠 我嚇到喊左出聲 都仲同自己講 好彩隻狗吠你 唔係你就行錯路啦<br />\n<br />\n我已經keep住日日咁樣安慰自己 但係都仲係好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一出發已經帶